{"tid":812453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求 排隊都要考牌","createTime":"2018-09-09T15:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T18:33:14.000Z","uid":203333,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa4ed9091c6a9ae17c2b25e9567e6dd4ca17a57","tid":812453,"uid":203333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"成日等巴士個陣，啲人成日排到幾條隊痴埋一齊，<br />\n架巴士黎到，條隊啲人又唔撚行，先知原來係排緊另一條，搞到要上啲人又行唔到前<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次試過排的士隊，排隊就一個跟一個啦，係我前面個廢老，企係條隊隔離又隔勁撚遠以為佢唔係排隊啦，到我準備上的士個陣就屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008e94762a12f4fecabe9e192399e9eab99f5b90","tid":812453,"uid":203333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:18:50.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489023cf09eb37abafc8466a7d85f6ba961f8adc","tid":812453,"uid":83060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/002345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F002345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=86af50ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e6a03f97ec508cab909b992356518cc89101e6a","tid":812453,"uid":203333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489023cf09eb37abafc8466a7d85f6ba961f8adc","tid":812453,"uid":83060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/002345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F002345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=86af50ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"就係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3338374b59464264a6c18cb7bf969e04561b88c5","tid":812453,"uid":185513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:33:26.000Z","msg":"屌返佢轉頭，驚9"},{"pid":"cb947337b349b4785c26e6e7475ad9b4003f0587","tid":812453,"uid":83060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e6a03f97ec508cab909b992356518cc89101e6a","tid":812453,"uid":203333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489023cf09eb37abafc8466a7d85f6ba961f8adc","tid":812453,"uid":83060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/002345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F002345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=86af50ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"就係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:33:14.000Z","msg":"如果我排佢後仲可以用身位修正佢，等後面啲人知我跟佢後面，最慘係佢响好前，佢後面條友又唔醒水去修正返條隊，搞到其他人誤會，排咗去廢老後面，條隊一長先發現又嘈交。根本好多嘢可以避免，係人嘅質素無下限所致。"}]}